                &lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;SIMULZINE#3-cover-accordion-menu-generator&#34; src=&#34;/media/images/accordion.png&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
                &lt;p&gt;An accordion menu is an often used element by &lt;span class=&#34;caps&#34;&gt;GUI&lt;/span&gt; designers. It comes handy because it&amp;#8217;s a &amp;#8220;spacesaver&amp;#8221; in rich applications that need to have their content easily accessible. Especially in mobile devices, accordions menus are found everywhere. In this post I present an accordion menu generator for the krpano panorama viewer, that recently got compatible with mobile devices (through webGL or css3D). This is also my first open source project&amp;nbsp;:)&lt;/p&gt;            </content>
